            are owned by Daily Life Hacks and are protected by international
            copyright, trademark, patent, trade secret, and other intellectual
            property or proprietary rights laws.
        </p>

        <h2>3. User Conduct</h2>
        <p>
            You agree to use the Website only for lawful purposes. You agree not
            to take any action that might compromise the security of the
            Website, render the Website inaccessible to others, or otherwise
            cause damage to the Website or the Content. You agree not to add to,
            subtract from, or otherwise modify the Content, or to attempt to
